property.name: note
property.value:
For Footsteps, Grabs, Handholds, and Landings, we employed a "surface_index" parameter. In these cases, there's nothing on the main timeline, and instead we play the audio directly from the parameter.
The general plan design-wise was to get real granular with surface sounds in Celeste. We did get to design a lot of them, but time ran short in the end, hence the gaps here and there.
